HEADWORD: Polygonometry
<hw>Pol`y*go*nom"e*try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Polygon</ets> + <ets>-metry</ets>.]</ety> <def>The doctrine
